# Git 属性配置 — 跨平台换行符与二进制文件处理

## 换行符：统一 LF（与 .editorconfig 一致）
* text=auto eol=lf

## 二进制文件：禁止换行符转换和 diff
*.png    binary
*.jpg    binary
*.jpeg   binary
*.gif    binary
*.ico    binary
*.svg    binary
*.woff   binary
*.woff2  binary
*.ttf    binary
*.eot    binary

## 锁定文件：避免无效 diff
pnpm-lock.yaml -diff
